OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782753500
OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Csexual relationship with crime victim
OL,6,FA former South Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Fofficer has been jailed after
OL,8,Fadmitting to a sexual relationship
OL,9,Fwith a victim of crime.
OL,11,FChristopher Cave, 62, from Formby in
OL,12,FLiverpool, struck up the relationship
OL,13,Fwhile working as an officer in
OL,14,FNottinghamshire in 2004 and it
OL,15,Fcontinued until early 2011.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
