FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782753500
OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Csexual relationship with crime victim
OL,6,FHe went on to work for South Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice between 2010 and 2017 and then
OL,8,Freturned as part of a retirement
OL,9,Fscheme available to people who have
OL,10,Faccumulated more than 30 years of
OL,11,Fpolice work.
OL,13,FThe allegations about the relationship
OL,14,Fcame to light in 2022 at which point
OL,15,FCave was arrested and suspended from
OL,16,Fduties.
OL,18,FHe resigned from the force in December
OL,19,F2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
