FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782753500
OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Csexual relationship with crime victim
OL,6,FDetective Constable Nicola Milner,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Cave crudely and blatantly
OL,8,Fabused the trust placed in him as a
OL,9,Fpolice officer and the victim in this
OL,10,Fcase remains at the forefront of our
OL,11,Fminds.
OL,13,F"His conduct fell well below the
OL,14,Fstandard that is expected of our
OL,15,Fofficers and we welcome the result of
OL,16,Ftoday's sentencing in court."
OL,18,FCave pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,19,Fmisconduct in a public office and was
OL,20,Fjaled for one year and nine months at
OL,21,FSheffield Crown Court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
