OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Csexual relationship with crime victim
OL,6,FAn internal misconduct process within
OL,7,Fthe force will go ahead now the
OL,8,Fcriminal proceeding have finished.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
